>Here's the situation.  I just bought a 78 Van 
  It ran for about 10 seconds, shut down and then
>would not fire again.  When I cranked it, it would
>almost catch, but not quite.  
> I do have spark, and I
>would assume fuel.....Hmmm!
>
>Thanks,
